less Disregard]]''\n|Meredith Craig\n|TV film\n|-\n|1987\n|''[[Murder, She Wrote]]''\n|Irene Rutledge\n|\"Simon Says, Color Me Dead\"\n|-\n|1987\n|''[[L.A. Law]]''\n|Patricia Pittman\n|\"Sparky Brackman R.I.P. ????-1987\"\n|-\n|1987\n|''Daddy''\n|Ann Burnette\n|TV film\n|-\n|1988\n|''[[Little Girl Lost (film)|Little Girl Lost]]''\n|Clara Brady\n|TV film\n|-\n|1989\n|''[[Unconquered (1989 film)|Unconquered]]''\n|Mary Flowers\n|TV film\n|-\n|1989\n|''Incident at Dark River''\n|Betty McFall\n|TV film\n|-\n|1990\n|''[[Thirtysomething]]''\n|Deborah\n|\"Post-Op\"\n|-\n|1992\n|''In the Line of Duty: Siege at Marion''\n|Vickie Singer\n|TV film\n|-\n|1992\n|''[[Willing to Kill: The Texas Cheerleader Story]]''\n|Verna Heath\n|TV film\n|-\n|1993\n|''[[The Hidden Room (1991\u20131993 anthology TV series)|The Hidden Room]]''\n|Dede\n|\"After the Crash\"\n|-\n|1994\u201395\n|''[[Christy (TV series)|Christy]]''\n|Fairlight Spencer\n|Main role\n|-\n|1995\n|''Death in Small Doses''\n|Asst. D.A. Jerri Sims\n|TV film\n|-\n|1996\n|''{{sortname|The|Road to Galveston|nolink=1}}''\n|Julia Archer\n|TV film\n|-\n|1996\n|''{{sortname|A|Stranger to Love|nolink=1}}''\n|Linda Grant\n|TV film\n|-\n|1997\n|''{{sortname|The|Killing Secret}}''\n|Tina Decapprio\n|TV film\n|-\n|1997\n|''[[Grace Under Fire]]''\n|Joan\n|\"Matthew's Old Lady\"\n|-\n|1997\n|''{{sortname|A|Child's Wish}}''\n|Joanna Chandler\n|TV film\n|-\n|1997\n|''[[Gun (TV series)|Gun]]''\n|Virginia\n|\"Ricochet\"\n|-\n|1997\n|''[[Walker, Texas Ranger]]''\n|Katie Malloy\n|\"Sons of Thunder\"\n|-\n|1997\n|''[[Cracker (U.S. TV series)|Cracker]]''\n|Lea Ann Garner\n|\"An American Dream\"\n|-\n|1998\u201300\n|''[[Early Edition]]''\n|Lois Hobson\n|Recurring role\n|-\n|1999\n|''[[Beyond the Prairie: The True Story of Laura Ingalls Wilder|Beyond the Prairie]]''\n|Narrator / Older [[Laura Ingalls Wilder]]\n|TV film\n|-\n|2000\n|''[[Touched by an Angel]]''\n|Betsy Baxter\n|\"The Empty Chair\"\n|-\n|2001\n|''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]''\n